title: [Kraken's Fall, Third Pier]
description: Blue and red arrows painted upon the smooth planks of the dock point to the northeast, while a solid green arrow points to the southeast.  A pair of sturdy steps leads down to a finger pier with five docking slips, a small sign next to them proclaiming "Slips 1-5," while heavy rope woven through holes in the support posts creates a flimsy railing.  Unseen in the dark sky, circling gulls lend their squabbling voice to the air.
